Software that downloads tiles in given areas

JTileDownloader - Java application to download and update tiles
maps4glopus     - Shell / perl scripts that use taho to create background maps
                  for Glopus (http://www.glopus.de)
taho            - Fetches a given set of tiles and creates calibration files
                  for Glopus, OziExplorer and various other programs
tiles_by_bbox   - Fetches tiles in a given bounding box

